So working on the same website for several days can be taxing.
Especially when you want to do it all in one night.
Take breaks. At night go sleep.
This page is for all your notes.

feel like you've done something that might need explaining in the future?
make a note

Feel like you don't want to go sleep because you'll forget where you are at?
make a note

To make a note is simple.
Create a note # and then add your note.

eg.

#1: This is your first official note.

Now all you have to do is reference the note number in a comment next to anything that needs explaining
Across all your files! 
Reference the note in a comment and then head back to this page to see exactly what the note easy.
Really is that simple hey.


Now go to bed!